text:
Stefanie Tücking (1 April 1962  – 1 December 2018) was a German radio and television presenter. She was born in Kaiserslautern, Germany. In Germany, Tücking worked for the German broadcaster Südwestrundfunk (SWR) as a television and radio presenter.
Tücking was found dead in Baden-Baden, Germany on 1 December 2018 at the age of 56.
